docs {
  Bruno collection for the Ringtail daemon HTTP + MCP surface.
  Kept in lockstep with services/daemon/src/index.ts and openapi.yaml
  (see CLAUDE.md "Docs are part of done"). One .bru per real route.

  Set `baseUrl` and `token` in the `local` environment from the daemon boot
  line (`ringtail up` prints the MCP URL + session token). Never hardcode the port.
}
